lead_paragraph: Alabama, Michigan, Clemson and Washington are at the top of The Associated Press Top 25 college football poll and the Big 12 was left without a top-10 team after a weekend during which four unbeaten teams lost.

headline.print_headline: AP Top 25: Alabama, Michigan, Clemson, Washington at Top
